<h2>You're Invited!</h2>

<p>Hi there! 👋</p>

<p><strong>{{inviterName}}</strong> has invited you to join <strong>{{tenantName}}</strong> as a <strong>{{role}}</strong>.</p>

<div class="info-box">
  <p><strong>🏢 Organization:</strong> {{tenantName}}</p>
  <p><strong>👤 Role:</strong> {{role}}</p>
  <p><strong>🏪 Store Access:</strong> {{#if storeNames}}{{storeNames}}{{else}}All stores{{/if}}</p>
</div>

<p>Click the button below to accept the invitation:</p>

<a href="{{inviteLink}}" class="btn btn-primary">Accept Invitation</a>

<div class="warning-box">
  <p><strong>⏰ This invitation expires in {{expiresIn}}</strong></p>
</div>

<p>If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
<p style="word-break: break-all; color: #667eea;">{{inviteLink}}</p>

<p>If you don't want to join this organization, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>The Coffee App Team</p>
